Watch Vault Pod:

bash
Copy
Edit
oc get pods -n cdp -w
Check Logs:

bash
Copy
Edit
oc logs -f vault-0 -n cdp
Check PVC Status:

bash
Copy
Edit
oc get pvc -n cdp
